            <thetext>All of our widgets offering selection like the list, table or tree are located in a scroll container. Scrolling such a container on a touch device results in a pointerdown on the touched item which currently results in a selection change. This might not the desired behavior because the user might only want to check out the rest of the widgets items. So we should change that to achieve a good user experience. The following widgets are affected:

SelectBox
VirtualSelectBox
ComboBox
VirtualComboBox
Tree
VirtualTree
TreeVirtual
List
VirtualList
Table</thetext>
